import Vue from 'vue'
import Router from 'vue-router'

import pay from '../module/common/pay'
import index from '../module/common/index'
import cropper from '../module/common/cropper'

import app from '../module/app/router'
import mine from '../module/mine/router'
import card from '../module/card/router'
import other from '../module/other/router'
import login from '../module/login/router'
import circle from '../module/circle/router'
import spread from '../module/spread/router'
import article from '../module/article/router'
import webPage from '../module/webPage/router'
import setting from '../module/setting/router'
import message from '../module/message/router'
import activity from '../module/activity/router'
import marketing from '../module/marketing/router'

let routes = [
  {
    path: '/',
    redirect: '/index'
  },
  {
    name: 'appHome',
    path: '/index',
    component: index,
    meta: {
      nav: true,
      auth: true,
      keepAlive: true,
      title: '汇营天下'
    }
  },
  {
    path: '/cropper',
    component: cropper,
    meta: {
      nav: false,
      auth: true,
      title: '上传图片'
    }
  },
  {
    name: 'pay',
    path: '/pay',
    component: pay,
    meta: {
      nav: false,
      auth: true,
      title: '支付',
      keepAlive: false
    }
  }
]
routes = routes.concat(
  app,
  card,
  mine,
  other,
  login,
  circle,
  spread,
  article,
  webPage,
  setting,
  message,
  marketing,
  activity
)

Vue.use(Router)
export default new Router({
  routes: routes,
  linkActiveClass: 'active'
})
